title: Artist Spotlight: John Karel (aka jjjjjjjjjjohn) and his Low-Poly Windows
description: Kevin is joined by John Karel (aka jjjjjjjjjjohn), the low-poly animation artist best known for OBJKT generative PFP project Randomly Common Skeles and the Window Still Life series on Hic Et Nunc.
